            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Has the Prime Minister seen the statement made by Lord Alexander in which he has said that the British nation has been kept in ignorance of what has been going on in Korea? And if the British nation has been kept in ignorance of the situation in Korea, has not Her Majesty's Government some responsibility?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
